[Method]
Dir
[Prefix]
dcl_ComboBox_
[Desc]
This method will fill the ComboBox with a list of files found in the directory search that matches the \cf1 sExtension \cf0 argument.  If the \cf1 sExtension \cf0 is not specified *.* is assumed.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName
\par\tab sDirectory
[as String]
\par\tab\i{Optional}\i0 sExtension
[as String]


