[Method]
Clear
[Prefix]
dcl_ComboBox_
[Desc]
This method will clear the ComboBox of all its items. If the combo box style is a pre-populated list, this method will cause the list to get reset and repopulated.
[Arguments]
ProjectFileName


[Method]
GetCount
